Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  這確實是我不帶任何虛假的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說幾遍都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡真尋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡…喜歡…喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看過來  今天我們去買禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們趕緊先四處逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來陪您  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種鄉下的禮品店裡能淘到什麼好東西呢  我好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是奈亞子  很有眼光嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要淘到個不得了的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  你臉很紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…20年前的遊戲居然還有新品還賣這麼便宜！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然總有地方會留有存貨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這樣子說不定還能淘到不少寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意的只有我一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢到極點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好罕見的遊戲機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.07,0:01:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是WonderTswan Crystal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.80,0:01:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想玩GUNPEY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道還能不能玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打開開關試試
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該在溫泉街啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起床  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋寶貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋寶貝真是的  叫了你好多次了卻毫無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊  再不快點就要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是高中生了  別讓人這麼操心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  這一連串的口吻到底是鬧哪樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  再不出門就真的要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最優先事項哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊趕緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說奈亞子她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是那幾個傢伙  說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你突然從轉角冒出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往哪裡看呢  你這變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那個…奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁不出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下任女王和龍神的巫女都當不成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\fad(0,450)}（私立心跳學園）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連學校也變奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安  八坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  八坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領帶系彎了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.77,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儀表必須得時刻注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿撒托斯大人一直看著我們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  八坂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千萬別放棄希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是覺得趕不上就放棄的話  比賽就真結束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太  連你也這樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢  八坂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  我是余市健彥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想知道女生們的訊息  可以隨時來問我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}喲  我是余市健彥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余市  我明明相信著唯有你是不會變的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}如果你想知道女生們的訊  訊  訊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  八坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮井！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒變奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是平時的你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  女生們對你的好感度是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,160)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}奈亞子  進擊love heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,165)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}蓮太  一萬兩千年前就想與你合體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(160,260)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}克子  勇往墮落  desire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,265)\fs16\1c000000\bord0\shad0}珠緒  認真戀愛前555秒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些什麼玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了  八坂真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話跟你說  過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說連露西也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？這是在遊戲裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  現在你被捲進了受詛咒的戀愛模擬遊戲「心跳高中」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被捲進了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是那台遊戲機的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從遊戲外面連接進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捲進遊戲的人會被分配到各種戀愛模擬的角色設定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此那些傢伙才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不知道是何種力量造成如此事態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有這點是不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若不能和某位角色一起迎來圓滿的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就永遠無法離開這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以攻略的角色有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞拉托提普
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克圖格亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮井珠緒  這四人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須和其中某位成為戀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼蓮太也在其中…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也維持不了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八坂真尋  要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後  在遊戲中發生任何事情  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於知道真相了嗎  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  想要離開這裡就只有委屈自己接受Galgame式的世界觀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之…現在無論豎起怎樣的Flag  真尋都會積極配合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧劇到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把少年隨便和蓮太什麼的撮合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就和奈亞子在這裡無盡的八月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這角色設定果然不太適合我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但難得在遊戲裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再主動點也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3c7A2BE3\shad0\fscx75\bord6}奈亞子的「心跳高中」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3cFFFFFF\shad0\fscx75}奈亞子的「心跳高中」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是戀愛模擬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋…哦呀不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八坂同學～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明顯是在裝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢我不明白喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想揍你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊進入下個劇情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.09,0:08:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點豎起一堆我的Flag吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  超級奈亞子醬時間開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用英語來說就是「Quick Start」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,225)\fs16}（別輸　活下去）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個劇情是游泳課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  我馬上就要溺水了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴對嘴拜託了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大聲宣言！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  嘴對嘴的話就由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴對胸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴對腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴對…嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你給我適可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官配女主角在溺水之前就遇到危機啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真尋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為蓮太同學突然倒下了  八坂同學扛著他去保健室了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  真…真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  蓮太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(399,323)\fs20}Final fusion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們一定要最終融合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想要真尋的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮太  你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇情變更了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼時候變的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經厭倦了…一成不變的觀察對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(342,323)\fs20}Humanoid Interface
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會通過強硬手段誘使資訊爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後根據觀測到的狀況收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設定…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為自己是哪位班長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要殺了你來看看奈亞子的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.05,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移到下個劇情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回又是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心懷對真尋的感情  我在此歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪神Knows
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不住嘴  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好的那個超棒作畫的著名場景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立心跳學園
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立心跳學園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到家庭餐廳Derleth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回又在打工了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了猛地提高好感度所必須的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去向店長遞交辭職信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著  一不小心和店長扯上關係的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被手持日本刀的美女店員給一刀兩半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去  客人叫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人  請別瞎按
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問需要什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒這功能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來奈亞子線搞破壞是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子  你好可愛  好想就這麼綁了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想凌辱你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的身體調教得離了我就活不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那傾述你歪曲的思想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想穿和你一樣的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這制服不適合你這種胸部這麼小的穿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都不小哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…我怎麼覺得台詞被人搶了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  真尋寶貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新感覺治癒系媽媽會為你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了媽媽  我差不多什麼都知道了  不用硬撐角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  還以為能和小尋相親相愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你想好和誰迎來結局了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不能含糊  到時候說不定余市來向你告白…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要那種Bad End
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好歹是為了從遊戲中逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湊合選一個如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  畢竟我會被人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果太隨意的話  總覺得有點說不過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  你說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  我是余市健彥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想知道女生們的訊息  可以隨時來問我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前推薦的約會地點是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  下雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回又是聖誕節了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌控浪漫的邪神似乎在祝福我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不應該是詛咒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手工製作的蓮太哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是用來陪睡  還是一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任君使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過cast off需要你自行負責哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙CQC  智慧袋5號
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時打火機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是便利的近身格鬥術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子也有東西給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替我轉交奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己穿過一次之後再給她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲  我滑倒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚登記表
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你送上我的下半生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的flag！官方手續啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想趁機渾水摸魚製造社會性的既成事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有其他禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親手織的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合適哦  真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豎起決定性的flag了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然  畢竟全心全意傾注在其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定是和我的結局了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別瞎說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能就這麼決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總喜歡糾結些奇怪的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我就喜歡你這點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  既然如此只能決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉其他對手  那麼結局就只有一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終劇情為肉搏戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「血腥情人節」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛模擬遊戲最後的伏線回收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞著真尋的貞操
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們戰個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你和少年雙宿雙飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好不過  順從著狂奔的本能  覺醒吧靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不戰便無法存活到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與真尋的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真尋的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奈亞子的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.67,0:17:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結局是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八坂同學是第一次這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  雖然有點煞風景了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是搞不懂現在啥情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:17:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在體育場庫和女孩獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門不知道被誰給鎖上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不過上一夜的孤男寡女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這超速展開得也太過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是18X了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  失敗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想來個出其不意扭轉局勢的結局呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  少瞎胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒胡鬧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是真的喜歡八坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暮井…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想立flag嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  露餡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此生無恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底來的會是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別好的不靈壞的靈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果來的人真是余市…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真尋  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了哦  耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了這最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了迎接圓滿的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得在這貌似有什麼傳說的樹下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許下永恆的一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這是遊戲裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這種事我怎麼可能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不這樣的話  就無法逃離這個世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是做不到！這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請接受我這份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直努力就是為了這一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.64,0:20:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亞子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡真尋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了從遊戲中逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了從遊戲中逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.60,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了從遊戲中逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來買禮物  然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來平安無事地歸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子把遊戲裡發生的事都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  八坂真尋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真尋你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉好紅喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.97,0:21:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  買完東西了吧  差不多該回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都買了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.05,0:21:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:21:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  到底怎麼回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你那表情就知道一定有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  真的沒什麼啦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於又輪到我和真尋做預告了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.92,0:23:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.76,0:23:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到吧  下一話的舞台居然是在尾道市
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分為三部曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說些啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話「我是他  他是我」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.15,0:23:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有兩部呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樣中…（學生）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我打住


